attr.title: Farm Keeper
attr.desc: A tile-based farming game where success means maximizing yields to survive the rent, expanding your farm through random tile choices.
attr.inst: Purchase the game on Steam and copy the FarmKeeper.pck into gamedata folder. You can also use the free demo version.
attr.inst_md: Purchase the game on [Steam](https://store.steampowered.com/app/2458940/Farm_Keeper/) and copy the `FarmKeeper.pck` into `gamedata` folder. You can also use the free `demo` version.
